---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="P1 Express">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-4 tracking-tight">P1 Express</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mb-12">
        What if the P1.express method could live inside a small, lightweight app
        that you fully own?
    </p>

    <article class="prose prose-lg prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            That simple question sparked the creation of <strong
                >P1express.app</strong
            >. A minimal, offline-first implementation built for people who want
            to focus on what truly matters—planning, doing, and
            reflecting—without distractions.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-12 mb-6">A Personal Philosophy</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            As a developer, I have always been fascinated by how technology can
            serve people. When I discovered the P1.express method, something
            clicked. Its simplicity, structure, and rhythm reminded me why I
            started coding: to build things that make life easier.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            I wanted to turn that philosophy into something you can use.
            Something personal. Something private. Something fully yours.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-12 mb-6">No Accounts. No Servers.</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            To deliver on that promise, I adopted a strict "Digital Minimalism"
            approach. I didn't just build an app <em>for</em> the method; I built
            an app <em>like</em> the method.
        </p>

        <ul class="list-none pl-0 space-y-6">
            <li
                class="pl-4 border-l-4 border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
            >
                <strong class="block text-xl mb-2">Zero Dependencies</strong>
                <span class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    No frameworks. No complex build pipelines. Just pure,
                    performant Vanilla JavaScript. This ensures the app will
                    work today, tomorrow, and ten years from now.
                </span>
            </li>
            <li
                class="pl-4 border-l-4 border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
            >
                <strong class="block text-xl mb-2">Offline First</strong>
                <span class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    The app lives entirely in your browser. No data collection.
                    No sync issues. This ensures absolute privacy and instant
                    speed.
                </span>
            </li>
            <li
                class="pl-4 border-l-4 border-neutral-300 dark:border-neutral-700"
            >
                <strong class="block text-xl mb-2">The 117KB Monolith</strong>
                <span class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    A single HTML file that you download and run locally. It's
                    smaller than most web images, yet contains everything you
                    need.
                </span>
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-12 mb-6">Philosophy in Code</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Every technical choice was made to align with a core principle of
            the P1 Express method.
        </p>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
                <thead>
                    <tr
                        class="border-b border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800"
                    >
                        <th
                            class="py-4 font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
                            >Method Principle</th
                        >
                        <th
                            class="py-4 font-bold text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
                            >Technical Execution</th
                        >
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                    <tr
                        class="border-b border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-900"
                    >
                        <td class="py-4 pr-4"><strong>Simplicity</strong></td>
                        <td class="py-4"
                            >Zero dependencies, single file architecture.</td
                        >
                    </tr>
                    <tr
                        class="border-b border-neutral-100 dark:border-neutral-900"
                    >
                        <td class="py-4 pr-4"><strong>Focus</strong></td>
                        <td class="py-4"
                            >Instant load, no network latency, no spinners.</td
                        >
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="py-4 pr-4"><strong>Control</strong></td>
                        <td class="py-4">100% Local data ownership.</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-12 mb-6">More Than a Tool</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            P1express.app is a way to bring the method we love into daily
            practice. To act with focus, awareness, and simplicity—even in a
            noisy world.
        </p>

        <a
            href="https://www.p1express.app"
            target="_blank"
            class="no-underline block border-2 border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-900 hover:border-neutral-300 dark:hover:border-neutral-600 transition-all my-8"
        >
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <div>
                    <span
                        class="font-bold text-xl text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100"
                        >p1express.app</span
                    >
                    <p
                        class="text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 m-0 mt-2"
                    >
                        Download the app
                    </p>
                </div>
                <span class="text-2xl text-neutral-500">↗</span>
            </div>
        </a>

        <p class="text-base text-neutral-500 mt-12">
            Learn more about the methodology at <a
                href="https://omimo.org/en/modules/p1.express/"
                target="_blank"
                class="underline hover:text-neutral-800 dark:hover:text-neutral-200"
                >omimo.org</a
            >.
        </p>
    </article>
</Layout>
